/data/users/chjing/slurm-nvgpufreq/README.md:68:optional   /path/to/nvgpufreq.so
/data/users/chjing/slurm-nvgpufreq/README.md:71:When a user wants to use the plugin must submit a job specify the _nvgpufreq_ gres and the exclusivity of the job.
/data/users/chjing/slurm-nvgpufreq/README.md:73:sbatch $SLURM_CONF --gres=nvgpufreq --exclusive $BIN
